The folder structure:
cmd/api/          # HTTP server entrypoint
internal/
  â”œâ”€â”€ handler/    # HTTP â†’ Service
  â”œâ”€â”€ service/    # Business logic
  â”œâ”€â”€ repository/ # Service â†’ Database
  â”œâ”€â”€ domain/     # Core entities
  â””â”€â”€ dto/        # API contracts

